title: CONGRATULATIONS TO LEXI AND ANNIE!
content: Congratulations are in order to Lexi as she was selected this past week to represent our community for the coming year as a member of the royal court for the Hunters Community Fair!  Congrats Lexi!!  We know you will do a great job!  Also…Ed K. has always been a “King” but now he has a daughter who is a “princess” as Annie was also selected to be royalty.  Congrats to you Ed.
